<style src="./NavAreasComponent.css"></style>
<template src="./NavAreasComponent.html"></template>
<script>
    export default {
        name: "NavAreasComponent",
        inject: ["areaList"],
        computed: {
            areasList() {
                let n_areaList = [];
                for (let i=2; i<this.areaList.length; i++) {
                    n_areaList[i-2] = this.areaList[i]; 
                }
                return n_areaList;
            }
        },
    }
</script>
